{"tid":1426521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"881 郭榮鏗講今日法律界遊行係矛頭轉移番比律政司，我覺得係十分正確既做法","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:18:06.000Z","uid":251292,"like":280,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"a98898fb654792e33c483a847c32d5a4992f9164","tid":1426521,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"首先呢幾日勇武已經比林鄭spin左去警民衝突<br />\n咁樣勇武落去係好易比政府轉移視線<br />\n根源其實就係呢個政府，我諗大家都明<br />\n尤其律政司呢個司法機關，亂告暴動罪<br />\n郭榮鏗話係要轉移番個矛頭比番政府<br />\n仲話有消息係指律政司原本係打算成立獨立檢控組，但比鄭若驊條仆街一野ban左 然後自己決定告45位暴動罪<br />\n今日就遊行，坐到等個條八婆出黎對質！<br />\n大家唔該煲大佢！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8900c52a44ebdacb734efda2a7cac054418deb9","tid":1426521,"uid":101392,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:41:47.000Z","msg":"推！必須對返準律政司"},{"pid":"d24742b9937df46b64204d18e77c68937bd5a57d","tid":1426521,"uid":251292,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"推呀！<br />\n宜家法律界都黎遊行唔通又廢青暴徒？<br />\n鄭若驊出黎呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0fdd90b4091d8871d35714df373718453728b2","tid":1426521,"uid":251292,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:42:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須對準律政司！必須對準林鄭！<br />\n等佢冇得再spin！！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9972db3c3affad5f3eda293299cee4bcc3362c5e","tid":1426521,"uid":251292,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"宜家成班法律界人士搵你對質呀！<br />\n出黎啦！龜縮左咁多日！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9525da0b06fd15b8b651f329